## EmbeddableFactory.getDefaultInput() method

Can be used to get any default input, to be passed in to during the creation process. Default input will not be stored in a parent container, so any inherited input from a container will trump default input parameters.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
getDefaultInput(partial: Partial<TEmbeddableInput>): Partial<TEmbeddableInput>;
```

|  --- | --- | --- |
|  partial | <code>Partial&lt;TEmbeddableInput&gt;</code> |  |

<b>Returns:</b>

`Partial<TEmbeddableInput>`
